'''NGC 7027'''是一個極為年輕，且物質極為緻密的[[行星狀星雲|行星狀星雲]]<ref name="SalasEtAl">{{Cite journal|title=The ISO-SWS spectrum of planetary nebula NGC 7027|url=http://www.aanda.org/10.1051/0004-6361:20000435|last=Bernard Salas|first=J.|last2=Pottasch|first2=S. R.|date=2001-03|journal=[[天文与天体物理学报|Astronomy & Astrophysics]]|issue=3|doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20000435|volume=367|pages=949–958|bibcode=2001A&A...367..949B|issn=0004-6361|last3=Beintema|first3=D. A.|last4=Wesselius|first4=P. R.}}</ref>，距離地球約3000光年（920秒差距），位於[[天鵝座|天鵝座]]。該星雲於1878年由[[讓·瑪璉·愛德華·史提芬|讓·瑪璉·愛德華·史提芬]]使用[[馬賽天文台|馬賽天文台]]口徑31英吋望遠鏡發現，是最小的行星狀星雲之一，也是至今最被廣泛研究的<ref name="O'Meara">{{Cite book|title=Deep-Sky Companions: Hidden Treasures|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=a6VY0Q1zsJoC&pg=PA514&hl=zh-CN|publisher=[[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]]|date=2007-04-12|isbn=978-1-139-46373-7|language=en|first=Stephen James|last=O'Meara|pages=514}}</ref>。

==概要==
NGC 7027是可見光亮度最高的行星狀星雲之一<ref name="Kaler">{{Cite book|title=The Hundred Greatest Stars|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MXxBoLwu2QMC&pg=PT220&hl=zh-CN|publisher=[[施普林格科学+商业媒体|Springer Science & Business Media]]|date=2002-06-19|isbn=978-0-387-95436-3|language=en|first=James B.|last=Kaler|pages=133}}</ref>，年齡約600年<ref name="WatersEtAl">{{Cite book|title=Astrophysics and Space Science|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QG3dN6hpJwAC&pg=PA490&hl=zh-CN|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|date=1998-08-31|isbn=978-0-7923-5152-8|language=en|first=L. B. F. M.|last=Waters|first2=C.|last2=Waelkens|first3=Karel A. van der|last3=Hucht|first4=P. A.|last4=Zaal|pages=490}}</ref>。

該星雲的體積異常地小，只有約0.2 x 0.1光年，而大部分行星狀星雲直徑至少1光年<ref name="O'Meara516">{{Cite book|title=Deep-Sky Companions: Hidden Treasures|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=a6VY0Q1zsJoC&pg=PA514&hl=zh-CN|publisher=Cambridge University Press|date=2007-04-12|isbn=978-1-139-46373-7|language=en|first=Stephen James|last=O'Meara|pages=516}}</ref>。NGC 7027的形狀非常複雜，其中有一個由電離氣體形成的橢球區域<ref name="Kastner">{{Cite journal|title=Discovery of Extended X-Ray Emission from the Planetary Nebula NGC 7027 by the [ITAL]Chandra X-Ray Observatory[/ITAL]|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/319651|last=Kastner|first=Joel H.|last2=Vrtilek|first2=Saeqa D.|date=2001-04-01|journal=[[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]]|issue=2|doi=10.1086/319651|volume=550|pages=L189–L192|arxiv=astro-ph/0102468|last3=Soker|first3=Noam|access-date=2021-03-30|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202001857/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/319651}}</ref>包含在巨大的中性氣體雲中<ref name="Masson">{{Cite journal|title=The structure of NGC 7027 and a determination of its distance by measurement of proper motions|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/doi/10.1086/167011|last=Masson|first=Colin R.|date=1989-01|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|doi=10.1086/167011|volume=336|pages=294|language=en|bibcode=1989ApJ...336..294M|issn=0004-637X|access-date=2021-03-30|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417191223/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/doi/10.1086/167011}}</ref>。它的內層結構被半透明的外層氣體和塵埃覆蓋<ref name="NOAO">{{Cite web|title=NGC 7027|url=http://www.noao.edu/outreach/aop/observers/n7027.html|accessdate=2010-03-11|publisher=NOAO|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601223736/http://www.noao.edu/outreach/aop/observers/n7027.html|archivedate=2010-06-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。NGC 7027的形狀是一個扁長橢球形外殼，內有一個[[三叶草属|三葉草]]狀的[[光分解作用|光解]]區域<ref name="Kastner" />。NGC 7027的擴張速度為17 km/s<ref name="Masson" />。NGC 7027的中心區域有[[X射线|X射线]]輻射，代表該區域溫度極高<ref name="Kastner" />。而在橢球型星雲外為是一系列暗淡的藍色同心球狀外殼<ref name="HubbleSite1996">{{Cite news|title=Hubble Telescope Photo Reveals Stellar Death Process|date=1996-01-16|url=http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/1996/1996/05/|accessdate=2010-03-11|archivedate=2010-03-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100316181910/http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/1996/1996/05/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

NGC 7027中心的[[白矮星|白矮星]]周圍可能有[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]存在，因此成為星雲中心極高溫的熱源<ref name="Guradzian p464">{{Cite book|title=The Physics and Dynamics of Planetary Nebulae|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xxVkZBVIZeAC&pg=PP245&hl=zh-CN|publisher=Springer Berlin Heidelberg|date=1997-04-17|isbn=978-3-540-60965-0|language=en|first=Grigor A.|last=Gurzadyan|pages=464}}</ref>。該星雲內的白矮星質量可能是太陽的0.7倍，[[光度|光度]]為7700倍<ref name="Kaler" />。NGC 7027現正處於行星狀星雲演化極早期，星雲內的分子正被光解為個別原子，而原子則正被電離<ref name="HubbleSite">{{Cite news|title=Hubble Captures the Shrouds of Dying Stars|date=1998-03-18|url=http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/1998/11/background/|accessdate=2010-03-11|archivedate=2010-03-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100318052704/http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/1998/11/background/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

NGC 7027外圍大規模的暈結構質量約是太陽的3倍，為中心電離區質量的100倍。NGC 7027的前身星質量散失是質量在太陽數倍的恆星不會成為[[超新星|超新星]]的重要證據<ref name="O'Meara516" />。

NGC 7027中心的高溫恆星使它的[[光譜|光譜]]中有大量且高度電離的譜線<ref name="SalasEtAl" />。該星雲中富含[[碳|碳]]，在暴露於強烈[[紫外線|紫外線]]輻射中的緻密分子區中是相當引人注意的研究目標<ref name="LiuEtAl">{{Cite journal|title=An ISO Long Wavelength Spectrometer detection of CH in NGC 7027 and an HeH + upper limit|url=https://academic.oup.com/mnras/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/mnras/290.4.L71|last=Liu|first=X.- W.|last2=Barlow|first2=M. J.|date=1997-10-01|journal=[[皇家天文學會月報|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]]|issue=4|doi=10.1093/mnras/290.4.L71|volume=290|pages=L71–L75|language=en|bibcode=1997MNRAS.290L..71L|issn=0035-8711|last3=Dalgarno|first3=A.|last4=Tennyson|first4=J.|last5=Lim|first5=T.|last6=Swinyard|first6=B. M.|last7=Cernicharo|first7=J.|last8=Cox|first8=P.|last9=Baluteau|first9=J.- P.|access-date=2021-03-30|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306181925/https://academic.oup.com/mnras/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/mnras/290.4.L71}}</ref>。NGC 7027的光譜和其他尋常行星狀星雲相比，來自中性分子的譜線較少，這是因為分子的結構遭到強烈紫外線輻射摧毀<ref name="KwokSandford">{{Cite book|title=Organic Matter in Space (IAU S251)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EWURgHzF3DQC&pg=PA170&hl=zh-CN|publisher=Cambridge University Press|date=2008|isbn=978-0-521-88982-7|language=en|first=[[國際天文聯會|International Astronomical Union]]|last=Symposium|pages=170}}</ref>。NGC 7027內的離子有極高的[[电离能|電離位]]<ref name="Gurzadian p45">{{Cite book|title=The Physics and Dynamics of Planetary Nebulae|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xxVkZBVIZeAC&pg=PP245&hl=zh-CN|publisher=Springer Berlin Heidelberg|date=1997-04-17|isbn=978-3-540-60965-0|language=en|first=Grigor A.|last=Gurzadyan|pages=45}}</ref>，被認為是尋找可能存在於星際空間的[[氦合氢离子|HeH<sup>+</sup>]]分子的高度可能存在區域<ref name="LiuEtAl" />。目前已有[[聚合钻石纳米棒|聚合钻石纳米棒]]存在於NGC 7027內的證據<ref name="Reddy">{{Cite news|last=Reddy|first=Francis|title=Seeing red with nanodiamonds|newspaper=Astronomy.com|date=2006-01-17|url=http://www.astronomy.com/asy/default.aspx?c=a&id=3851|accessdate=2010-03-11|archivedate=2007-03-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311040510/http://www.astronomy.com/asy/default.aspx?c=a&id=3851|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]於1996年首次拍攝NGC 7027。在該次拍攝前它原本被認為是中心恆星溫度過低，不足以使任何氣體電離的原行星狀星雲；但現在已知它正處於行星狀星雲演化過程最早期階段<ref name="O'Meara516" />。它的中心恆星原始質量一般相信在3到4倍太陽質量之間<ref name="SalasEtAl" />。

使用口徑15公分望遠鏡以倍率50倍觀測它時會像一個相對偏藍的恆星，如果倍率達到180倍，其模糊的外觀使它得到「軟糖熊星雲」（Gummy Bear Nebula）的綽號<ref>{{Cite web|title=NGC 7027 - Gummy Bear Planetary Nebula|url=https://stargazerslounge.com/topic/278437-ngc-7027-gummy-bear-planetary-nebula/|accessdate=2019-04-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111011617/https://stargazerslounge.com/topic/278437-ngc-7027-gummy-bear-planetary-nebula/|archivedate=2018-01-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這是在使用業餘望遠鏡時盡可能以最高放大率觀測的最佳結果。

2019年4月，天文學家宣布在長期觀測後在太空中，尤其是在NGC 7027內部確認了[[氦合氢离子|氦合氢离子]]的存在。這是一種被認為在[[大爆炸|大爆炸]]後10萬年就形成的古老分子<ref name="EG-20190417">{{cite news|last=Fisher|first=Christine|title=NASA finally found evidence of the universe's earliest molecule - The elusive helium hydride was found 3,000 light-years away.|url=https://www.engadget.com/2019/04/17/nasa-sofia-detects-helium-hydride/|date=17 April 2019|work=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|accessdate=17 April 2018|archivedate=2019-06-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605224054/https://www.engadget.com/2019/04/17/nasa-sofia-detects-helium-hydride/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NAT-20190417">{{Cite journal|title=Astrophysical detection of the helium hydride ion HeH +|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-019-1090-x|last=Güsten|first=Rolf|last2=Wiesemeyer|first2=Helmut|date=2019-04|journal=[[自然_(期刊)|Nature]]|issue=7752|doi=10.1038/s41586-019-1090-x|volume=568|pages=357–359|language=en|issn=1476-4687|last3=Neufeld|first3=David|last4=Menten|first4=Karl M.|last5=Graf|first5=Urs U.|last6=Jacobs|first6=Karl|last7=Klein|first7=Bernd|last8=Ricken|first8=Oliver|last9=Risacher|first9=Christophe|access-date=2019-04-18|archive-date=2019-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418133113/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-019-1090-x}}</ref>。

